- Install GoLang
$ yaourt -S go

- Create a go file
$ touch main.go

- Compile and run Go program
$ go run main.go

- Compile and execute
$ go build
$ ./helloWorld

- Documentation
$  go doc fmt Printf

- Generating a package
$ export GOPATH=/home/thiago/Documents/Go/helloWorld/
$ go build -o helloWorld
$ ./helloWorld

- Testing
$ cd myPackages
$ go test